    "ArticleTitle": "Salmonella infections in the mouse model: host resistance factors and in vivo dynamics of bacterial spread and distribution in the tissues.",
    "Pagination": {
      "StartPage": "398",
      "EndPage": "405",
      "MedlinePgn": "398-405"
